"{\"uid\": \"tribuneindia.com-news-parisolympics2024-aman-sehrawat-cruzes-to-wrestling-bronze\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Rohit Mahajan in Paris Aman Sehrawat, 21 years old, the future of wrestling, did what was expected of him today - he crushed Puerto Rico's Darian Toi Cruz 13-5 to earn India's fifth bronze of the Paris Olympics, the sixth medal overall.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 22, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999986185742264, \"rank\": 1.3814277538969094e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 128, \"end\": 139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.999400325562144, \"rank\": 0.0005397605347712386, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\"}, {\"begin\": 171, \"end\": 176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9977512470462953, \"rank\": 0.002236246566202724, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rohit Mahajan\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 13}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 52, \"to\": 62}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestling\", \"from\": 66, \"to\": 75}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 192, \"to\": 210}, {\"ngram\": \"the sixth medal\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The night before, however, there was fear in the Indian camp - Sehrawat's weight had shot up to 62 kg through the day's three bouts, 5 kg above the limit of his weight class.\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 292, \"end\": 303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Camp\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Indian camp\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Camp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Camp\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 284}, {\"ngram\": \"Sehrawat's weight\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 323}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 62 kg\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"the day's three bouts\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"the limit\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 396}, {\"ngram\": \"his weight class\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had to lose five kilos,\\\" said Sehrawat, blood on his face and sweat on his body, moments after his win.\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 524, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five kilos\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"Sehrawat\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"blood\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"his face\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"his body\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 500}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"his win\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not sleep the whole night...\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I practised at night, too!\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the morning, I was within the 57 kg limit!\\\"\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"the 57 kg limit\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sehrawat, the only man in the Indian squad, was unfazed by Cruz's early attacks.\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 665, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9998897715847224, \"rank\": 0.00011023702388296106, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sehrawat\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"the only man\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 657}, {\"ngram\": \"Cruz's early attacks\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Puerto Rican grabbing his left leg; Sehrawat defended valiantly but conceded a point through a push-out.\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 720, \"end\": 732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Ricans\", \"score\": 0.996877850032995, \"rank\": 0.003129968996027964, \"text\": \"Puerto Rican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Ricans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Ricans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his left leg\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 754}, {\"ngram\": \"Sehrawat\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"a push-out\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruz again went for his legs, but now Sehrawat got hold of him and got two points - the Indian 2-1 up!\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 927, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cruz\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"his legs\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"Sehrawat\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"hold\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"two points\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruz wasn't giving up, though; he grabbed Sehrawat's legs and twisted him - two points.\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cruz\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"Sehrawat's legs\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sehrawat still had power and the strength of mind - he pushed Cruz out, and got two more points by taking him down.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1134, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sehrawat\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"the strength\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"Cruz\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"two more points\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another takedown, another two points, and he led 6-3 at the hooter.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another takedown\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"another two points\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"the hooter\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The second period was packed with action but less frenetic - Cruz seemed to be losing energy, Sehrawat drawing it from him.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The second period\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"less frenetic - Cruz\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"Sehrawat\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After some good defence by the Puerto Rican, Sehrawat powered into him - another takedown, two more points, and the Jhajjar lad was in control at 8-5.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1359, \"end\": 1371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Ricans\", \"score\": 0.996877850032995, \"rank\": 0.003129968996027964, \"text\": \"Puerto Rican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Ricans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Ricans\"}, {\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jhajjar\", \"score\": 0.9999999979834229, \"rank\": 1.908660054198053e-09, \"text\": \"Jhajjar\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jhajjar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jhajjar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some good defence\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"Sehrawat\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"another takedown\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"two more points\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Desperate, Cruz had no option but to go for the Indian's legs and paid for the desperation - more points for Sehrawat, and a medal was a certainty at 13-5.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1527, \"end\": 1533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9998897715847224, \"rank\": 0.00011023702388296106, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cruz\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"no option\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"the desperation - more points\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"Sehrawat\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"a certainty\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of it all, there was a bleeding wound on Sehrawat's face, but pride in his eyes.\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"a bleeding wound\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"Sehrawat's face\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"his eyes\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orphaned at 11, finding a second home at Delhi's Chhatrasal Stadium, the farmer's son from Jhajjar did what his idol Ravi Dahiya did at Tokyo 2020 - a medal in his very first Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1771, \"end\": 1776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"score\": 0.999999993475285, \"rank\": 6.524799584323149e-09, \"text\": \"Delhi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\"}, {\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jhajjar\", \"score\": 0.9999999979834229, \"rank\": 1.908660054198053e-09, \"text\": \"Jhajjar\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jhajjar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jhajjar\"}, {\"begin\": 1847, \"end\": 1858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ravi_Kumar_Dahiya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ravi Dahiya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ravi_Kumar_Dahiya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ravi_Kumar_Dahiya\"}, {\"begin\": 1866, \"end\": 1871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9997290227882976, \"rank\": 0.0002684914029252482, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a second home\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"the farmer's son\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"his idol\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1846}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"his very first Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Take your experience further with Premium access.Thought-provoking Opinions, Expert Analysis, In-depth Insights and other Member Only Benefits Already a Member?Sign In Now The Tribune, now published from Chandigarh, started publication on February 2, 1881, in Lahore (now in Pakistan).\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21